Class Worker

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.zcraft.quartzlib.core.QuartzComponent
      • fr.zcraft.quartzlib.components.worker.Worker
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandWorkers

    public abstract class Worker
extends QuartzComponent
    The base class for workers. A worker is a thread that can handle multiple tasks, which are executed in a queue.
